		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">OpenBSD security features</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The <b><a href="/wiki/OpenBSD" title="OpenBSD">OpenBSD</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Operating_system" title="Operating system">operating system</a> is noted for its <a href="/wiki/Computer_insecurity" title="Computer insecurity">security</a> focus and for the development of a number of <b>security features</b>.</p>
